<!-- Hero -->
<div class="page-hero">
  {% render 'breadcrumb', breadcrumb_title: 'About' %}
  <h1>About Rejoice</h1>
  <p>Called to dress God's people through movement, beauty, and worship</p>
</div>

<!-- Mission statement block -->
<div class="section" style="padding-bottom:0;">
  <div class="about-grid">
    <div class="about-visual fade-in">
      <div class="about-image-main">
        <img src="{{ 'about-dancers.jpg' | asset_url }}"
             alt="Rejoice Dance Ministry dancers in praise garments"
             style="width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;border-radius:var(--radius-lg);" />
      </div>
      <div class="about-stat-card">
        <div class="num">25+</div>
        <div class="label">Years of<br/>Ministry</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="about-text fade-in">
      <span class="eyebrow">Our Calling</span>
      <h2>Called to Dress God's People</h2>
      <p>Rejoice counts on the creative force in which our Lord Jesus gives us in that Blessed moment when we enter in the movement of the Holy Spirit dressed in Holy Garments to give Glory and Praise to the King of Kings, Lord of Lords Jesus Christ.</p>
      <p>All of our garments are inspired in the creation of the Tabernacle and the Holy Vestiment of Aaron. Rejoice looks within the scripture as a guide to use the best materials, Fabrics, Stones, adornments to give the garments their beauty and excellence.</p>
      <div class="scripture">
        "These are the garments which they shall make: a breast piece and an ephod and a robe and a tunic of checkered work, a turban and a sash, and they shall make holy garments for Aaron your brother and his sons, that he may minister as priest to Me." — Exodus 28:4
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- Inspiration scripture -->
<div class="section" style="padding-top:60px;padding-bottom:0;">
  <div class="mission-block fade-in">
    <h2>Inspired by Scripture</h2>
    <p>"They shall take the gold and the blue and the purple and the scarlet material and the fine linen." — Exodus 28:5</p>
    <p style="margin-top:16px;font-size:0.95rem;">The garments were made from the finest materials. All of our designs are inspired by the Holy Spirit.</p>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- Values grid -->
<div class="section" style="padding-bottom:0;">
  <div class="section-title fade-in">
    <span class="eyebrow">What Sets Us Apart</span>
    <h2>Our Values</h2>
    <div class="divider-purple"></div>
  </div>
  <div class="values-grid">
    <div class="value-card fade-in">
      <span class="v-icon"><svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="6" cy="6" r="3"/><circle cx="6" cy="18" r="3"/><path d="M20 4L8.12 15.88M14.47 14.48L20 20M8.12 8.12L12 12"/></svg></span>
      <h4>Handcrafted Quality</h4>
      <p>Every garment is sewn with care in our state-of-the-art sewing facility in Hialeah, FL — no shortcuts, only excellence for the Lord.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="value-card fade-in">
      <span class="v-icon"><svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M2 3h6a4 4 0 0 1 4 4v14a3 3 0 0 0-3-3H2z"/><path d="M22 3h-6a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v14a3 3 0 0 1 3-3h7z"/></svg></span>
      <h4>Scripture-Inspired</h4>
      <p>Our designs draw directly from Exodus 28 — the finest materials, stones, and adornments as described in God's Word.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="value-card fade-in">
      <span class="v-icon"><svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M17 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H5a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"/><circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"/><path d="M23 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87"/><path d="M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75"/></svg></span>
      <h4>All Sizes Welcome</h4>
      <p>XS through 4X — because every body is made to worship and every dancer deserves a garment made for them.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="value-card fade-in">
      <span class="v-icon"><svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M20.84 4.61a5.5 5.5 0 0 0-7.78 0L12 5.67l-1.06-1.06a5.5 5.5 0 0 0-7.78 7.78l1.06 1.06L12 21.23l7.78-7.78 1.06-1.06a5.5 5.5 0 0 0 0-7.78z"/></svg></span>
      <h4>Ministry-Driven</h4>
      <p>We don't just sell dancewear. We equip God's people to move freely and beautifully in His presence.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- Our Factory -->
<div class="section">
  <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:60px;align-items:center;">
    <div class="fade-in">
      <span class="eyebrow">Our Facility</span>
      <h2 style="font-family:'Montserrat',sans-serif;color:var(--purple-dark);font-size:clamp(1.6rem,3vw,2.2rem);margin-bottom:20px;">Our Factory</h2>
      <p style="color:var(--text-mid);line-height:1.85;margin-bottom:16px;">The Lord has Blessed us with a state of the art Sewing Facility which makes us unique. Our state of the art machinery and quality standards assures that our garment will be done with excellence for our Lord Jesus.</p>
      <p style="color:var(--text-mid);line-height:1.85;margin-bottom:28px;">The Lord has given a gift — <em>"Called to Dress God's People"</em>. Located in the heart of Hialeah, Florida, our facility is where inspiration meets craftsmanship.</p>
      <div style="display:flex;gap:32px;flex-wrap:wrap;">
        <div style="text-align:center;">
          <div style="font-family:'Montserrat',sans-serif;font-size:2rem;font-weight:900;color:var(--purple);">409+</div>
          <div style="font-size:0.78rem;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--text-muted);">Products</div>
        </div>
        <div style="text-align:center;">
          <div style="font-family:'Montserrat',sans-serif;font-size:2rem;font-weight:900;color:var(--purple);">25+</div>
          <div style="font-size:0.78rem;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--text-muted);">Years</div>
        </div>
        <div style="text-align:center;">
          <div style="font-family:'Montserrat',sans-serif;font-size:2rem;font-weight:900;color:var(--purple);">XS–4X</div>
          <div style="font-size:0.78rem;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--text-muted);">All Sizes</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="fade-in" style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--purple-soft),var(--purple-pale));border-radius:var(--radius-lg);padding:50px;text-align:center;border:1px solid var(--border);">
      <span style="font-size:5rem;display:block;margin-bottom:20px;">🧵</span>
      <h3 style="font-family:'Montserrat',sans-serif;color:var(--purple-dark);font-size:1.2rem;margin-bottom:12px;">Made to Order</h3>
      <p style="color:var(--text-mid);font-size:0.95rem;">Every garment custom-tailored for you.<br/>Priority Mail USPS 2–3 Day Shipping.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- CTA -->
<div class="section-full section-gray">
  <div style="max-width:700px;margin:0 auto;text-align:center;padding:20px 0;">
    <h2 class="fade-in" style="font-family:'Montserrat',sans-serif;color:var(--purple-dark);font-size:clamp(1.6rem,3vw,2.2rem);margin-bottom:16px;">Ready to Worship in Beauty?</h2>
    <p class="fade-in" style="color:var(--text-muted);margin-bottom:32px;">Explore our full collection of handcrafted praise &amp; worship dancewear.</p>
    <div style="display:flex;gap:16px;justify-content:center;flex-wrap:wrap;" class="fade-in">
      <a class="btn-primary" href="{{ routes.collections_url }}">Explore Collection</a>
      <a class="btn-secondary" href="{{ pages['contact'].url }}">Contact Us</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
@media (max-width: 768px) {
  .section > div[style*="grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr"] {
    grid-template-columns: 1fr !important;
    gap: 32px !important;
  }
}
</style>
